data.title: Here & Now; 1312
data.meta_description:
Here & Now, michelle Obama and chris christie visit wisconsin, OpenSOT.
Soundbites from Chris Christie in Hudson and Michelle Obama in Milwaukee
rallies. michelle Obama and chris christie visit wisconsin, Obama Christie
Tape. This is the story from Fred and Zac’s combined coverage of the
Governor Chris Christie rally in Hudson for Scott Walker and the Michelle
Obama rally in Milwaukee for Mary Burke. new poll results, Marquette
University Law School Pollster Charles Franklin. New poll out this week.
He’s in Madison. For governor's race and attorney general's race. 3 state
senate races to watch for control of legislature, State Senate Races to
Watch. This is Zac’s report on three State Senate races to watch for the
November election in regards to control of the legislature, PolitiFact # 9 -
Claims on job and job creation, Politifact # 9 - Milwaukee Journal Sentinel
PolitiFact reporter Dave Umhoefer joins us from Marquette polycom to review
the claims on jobs that the Mary Burke and Scott Walker campaigns repeat
over and over. That Wisconsin is 'dead last in the Midwest' for job growth
and that Mary Burke's time at commerce resulted in 130, 000 fewer jobs:
B-roll: excerpt of Burke TV ad against Walker campaign and Republican
Governors Association TV ad against Burke,
